Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:02.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you wish…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:06.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…would you like me to take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:11.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To the place in this city where wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Did you leave something at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:28.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I was just taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Reciting lines from a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:37.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a play that I want to perform when the drama club reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, so they were lines…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I always practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:46.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since you were here, I had you watch my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you're up to getting the drama club back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:56.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I can do,\Nbut I'm planning on giving it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:58.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:00.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.59,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The girl's life is a lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.85,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,No one other than the girl exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.39,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,It is a simple fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:57.00,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,…since there is neither birth nor death here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.83,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Such is this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.45,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,That body was made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.99,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Is a “wish” all that I need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.09,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,A wish to be born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.04,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The one and only warmth in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.39,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,I've sought that for quite some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.74,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,414)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.74,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}The First Step
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Getting the drama club back together…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, at least it'll be a good diversion for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.73,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya! Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.39,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.59,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:50.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not used to driving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I just got my license last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All right. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No dents. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll let you off without paying the repair fee. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You'd better be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:15.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't I the victim in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi Kyou, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,There are a lot of savage girls\Nin our school, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara. It's rare to see you at such a normal hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I like paying back debts quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Like the one I owe to that other savage girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.81,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was out of shape last time, but not today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When there's too much time between taking the mound,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,even the best pitcher…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,…can get knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's a really lame analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.34,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Take my advice and stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.14,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Or do you not mind becoming unable to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:05.44,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I wonder which one of us\Nwill be unable to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.68,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.39,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Will you be my witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.32,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,That this is for self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, since it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:15.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.50,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.09,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Do you want me to make you unable to stand for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You can't possibly do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Quit blabbering and bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wow, he's getting air time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.21,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Acquaintance! The dust chute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.47,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You'll fall if I release these fingers. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.52,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Do you want to fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.38,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I didn't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.08,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Did I go too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure he's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:11.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! Sunohara! You alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Screw you! This isn't the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.43,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I really wish this were the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.64,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But… seeing you guys brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.44,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Never mind. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.52,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Forget what I said. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.90,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You saw it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, so she really does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,She was just here in this hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The ghost of a female student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:47.97,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,She walks up to you and gives you a cursed item.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.50,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,At a glance, she's a normal girl, but something's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is the door unlocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.01,Note,Oka,0,0,0,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Perfect. I'll take a nap here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That book belongs here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can't go cutting it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're reading hard stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you skipping class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And why are you barefoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.43,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.52,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This is the one most well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Food is off-limits in the library, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Do you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, since you offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I only have one pair of chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'd better clean up now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,since class will start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You still need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.19,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:36.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is she the ghost of the girl that got in an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.95,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,That's probably Ichinose Kotomi-san from Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ichinose Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:46.56,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,She's a genius girl who ranks in the top ten in every subject in the national exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:51.43,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I hear that she does independent studies instead of attending classes, and the school doesn't have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.63,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,She's famous within the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A genius girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No wonder she was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Fujibayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:03.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your sister! It's no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.35,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, she comes to school on her bi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.85,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come with me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.65,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,“Bi”? What bi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.90,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,“Bi”?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing\Nsaying that in the middle of class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“What?” The fact that you ride a bi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.40,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Do you want to get me suspended from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You know commuting to school by bike is prohibited, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:36.34,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun, what were you talking about with Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi Kyou in class E is bi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.09,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.58,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,“Bi”?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Bi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.33,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,She does it with guys and girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.51,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, she is kind of masculine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.63,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.74,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, is what he said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why are you believing him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.37,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's “bike”! We were talking about the scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Cleaning duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're alone? {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll finish it right away, so please wait in the club room. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We need to get members or else we won't get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's make a flier for recruiting members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:57.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It'd be good to make the date after the Founders Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:58.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.05,Note,,0,0,0,,Join the Drama Club - Open House May 15th - President Furukawa Nagisa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't it missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:12.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about adding, “The cutest president on campus will be waiting”?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The cutest president on campus will…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:28.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you write that, some stupid guys might fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want people to come for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Besides, you're more suitable as the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you yesterday that I'm only helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:42.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if the drama club goes active, I won't join.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to be the center of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The president makes the final decision in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You even have a play you want to perform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, will I be able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Get your act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can write this flier as you like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,As I like…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:09.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then, can I draw an illustration that I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:14.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure. Only words would be too bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:23.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dango, dango, dango, dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The great big dango family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's something that was popular a while back…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes! The Big Dango Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:42.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why the Big Dango Family of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It died off a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But it's still cute to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You don't think it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ahh, if you think it's good, then go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I did say to do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Pork cutlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is a charm to cheer myself on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:11.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's to give myself a favorite dish as a reward if I can do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Rather than pork cutlet, let's get\Na Big Dango Family and bring it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After we get the fliers posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:25.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have way too much time on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:30.69,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.43,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,D-Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is this the art club's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then are you working on your art homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.70,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:16.19,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,This is Fuuko's favorite…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The blade's chipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's dangerous for you to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.06,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Make sure you only use sharp knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll find some in the art studio, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.69,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your hand hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.99,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.36,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See, it does hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.92,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give me five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The thing where you slap hands\Nafter you make a shot in basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.87,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko knows! Fuuko's seen it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. Give me five then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:11.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.69,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Dribble…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.77,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:15.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need to go from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:17.34,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko made it! {ep1 with change}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:22.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See, it does hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:38.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,“Join the Drama Club”?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, you're involved in something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And what have you been doing up till now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.87,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Training to beat Sakagami Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But, the drama club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:55.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm surprised to see you interested in something dumb like a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:02.80,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You've always hated people involved in club activities so much it made you want to puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:07.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Well, you'll have to fill me in on the details soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:17.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you don't like club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was a meaningless conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can't do much about it if they don't sell them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:32.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, these have got to be better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.21,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.22,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,What are you doing with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm giving them to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.87,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,Will you let me help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.68,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.48,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,Will you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's with talking to me like I'm a stranger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What am I to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.76,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn it. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:17.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not the real thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It really is a big family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wish I could join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:52.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was depressed all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:59.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,During the cleaning, I was originally working with everyone in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But before I knew it, I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:02.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've always been clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:11.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've been teased by others like that since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:15.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thanks to Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What I was talking about earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara and I both enrolled to play sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know about enrolling to play sports, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara came for soccer, and I came for basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I quit soon after enrolling in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's a little story behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You came to not like basketball anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…I haven't touched a ball in a while, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:56.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, in that case, would you like to play basketball with me after school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:01.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you\Non the court tomorrow after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's play some basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…in that case, would you like to play basketball with me after school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, let's skip school today. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's Saturday, so it's a half day anyway. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why do you keep looking out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing your umbrella, Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She wouldn't be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's raining, so you should have gone home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:21.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But we would have missed each other if you had come when I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There was no proof that I'd come, was there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But you did come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:32.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You always help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I wanted to at least be able to play basketball with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are we going to do in this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then, let me see you take a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:52.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've never seen a shot from a basketball player up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You take a position like this and shoot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:00.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You won't shoot underhand like I would, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My right arm doesn't go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:37.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I got in a fight with my pops when I was in my third year of middle school and injured my right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:40.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My arm won't go any higher than my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't play basketball anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:51.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I… I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:58.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I… keep… troubling… you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:06.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa.
