Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:37.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:46.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You may be an idiot, but I don't think there's anything wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:53.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. My guess is that you don't\Ndeal with that stuff very well, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:23:55.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:57.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I usually say exactly what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:58.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:01.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It hurts sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So believe in your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:05.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:07.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Furukawa Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:09.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
